dc_title_s: St. Albans by the Sea, Ocean County, New Jersey
dc_description_s: This map is a plan for St Albans in Ocean County. It includes numbered blocks, property lots, and labelled road names. More information about the area's location and attractions is provided along the right side of the map. In the upper left hand corner a map of the state shows the area's location in New Jersey.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
